<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Smell of ground coffee and in the cup</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Flavour</td>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Tasting notes in the mouth</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Aftertaste</td>
