</tr>
<tr>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Body</td>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Texture, weight in the mouth</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Balance</td>
<td class="py-3 pr-4 border-b border-black/20">Harmony between all elements</td>
