<h2 class="font-typewriter text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 mt-12">Conclusion: Commercial or Specialty?</h2>
<p class="mb-4">There&#39;s no right answer. It depends on what you&#39;re looking for:</p>
<p class="mb-4"><strong>Commercial coffee works if:</strong></p>
