<li>You want quick, cheap caffeine</li>
<li>You don&#39;t care much about flavour</li>
<li>Coffee is a habit, not a pleasure</li>
</ul>
<p class="mb-4"><strong>Speciality coffee works if:</strong></p>
<ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
<li>You enjoy flavour and want to explore it</li>
<li>You value knowing where what you consume comes from</li>
<li>You&#39;re willing to pay a bit more for quality</li>
<li>You care that the producer receives a fair price</li>
</ul>
